                        @* cURL *@
                        <pre class="lf-code-pre lf-code-snippet" id="lf-snippet-curl"><code><span class="lf-ln"> 1</span>  curl -X POST <span class="lf-str">"https://api.boldsign.com/v1/template/send?templateId={YOUR_TEMPLATE_ID}"</span> \
